    "answer_id" : 18852484,
    "question_id" : 18852425,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you open your module settings (<strong>F4</strong>) you can nominate which paths contain 'source'. Intellij will then mark these directories in blue and allow you to add classes etc.</p>\n\n<p>In a similar fashion you can highlight test directories for unit tests.</p>\n"
