    "body" : "<p>Had this issue too. Invalidating Caches/Restart did the trick for me. Please upvote so the the IntelliJ folks take this more seriously. This gives the IDE a terrible UI/UX experience.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://youtrack.jetbrains.com/issue/IDEA-203100\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://youtrack.jetbrains.com/issue/IDEA-203100</a></p>\n"
