    "question_id" : 18852425,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I will share another interesting point. If you try to create a package with the reserved keyword then it will be treated as a normal directory and not a package. I was having this issue where I was creating a package named import and it was converting that to a directory.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/NhnWw.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/NhnWw.png\" alt=\"A sample of mine\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
